text: The 2019 Chinese FA Women's Cup () is the 13th edition of the Chinese FA Women's Cup. Jiangsu Suning are the defending champions. It is held from 16 March to 22 June 2019. ==First Round== ==Second Round== ==Quarter-Finals== ==Semi-Finals== ===1st Leg=== ===2nd Leg=== ==Finals== ===1st Leg=== ===2nd Leg=== ==References== Category:2019 in Chinese football
